    Disclaimer
    This customization app is an art creation tool for fun. Minting your creations onchain have no intrinsic value or expectation of financial return. The NPC used for redeeming a custom creation onchain and the art itself are completely useless and for entertainment purposes only. All art created via the app can easily be copied-and-saved, so minting is completely optional. There is no formal team and no roadmap for this app, so use it purely for fun at your own discretion.
